    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* 机器翻译说明，游戏为英文。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这是一款什么游戏？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spiritus Vindicta》是一款趣味十足的游戏，为不断扩展的捉鬼类型带来了全新的 2D 单人游戏体验。游戏故事情节简单，玩家要寻找并驱除改变了一切的幽灵。在整个旅途中，您将前往众多闹鬼地点执行任务，调查潜伏在那里的鬼魂。在探索每个地点时，您都需要找到并记录证据，以便了解鬼魂的情况以及驱除它们的方法。体验在恐惧中寻找的感觉，同时努力保持冷静，最重要的是要活着。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>期待什么</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于那些熟悉捉鬼类型游戏的人来说，您可能会对在环境中探索证据，同时努力在捉鬼行动中幸存下来感到如鱼得水。不过，你会注意到一些不同之处，因为这款游戏的目标是不那么逼真，节奏稍快。一路上仍会有一些惊吓，但体验的基调更像传统游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 调查并驱除 10 种不同类型的鬼魂</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 体验不同的鬼魂攻击，它们在故事过程中会变得更加危险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162260/extras/8dd5631be40eaa63864e549aae62b2ea.poster.avif?t=1740533602\" width=442 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162260/extras/8dd5631be40eaa63864e549aae62b2ea.webm?t=1740533602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162260/extras/8dd5631be40eaa63864e549aae62b2ea.mp4?t=1740533602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 准备好躲避鬼魂的追捕</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162260/extras/a4c8a1c0d2c55170a9c134d72f7c1523.poster.avif?t=1740533602\" width=442 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162260/extras/a4c8a1c0d2c55170a9c134d72f7c1523.webm?t=1740533602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162260/extras/a4c8a1c0d2c55170a9c134d72f7c1523.mp4?t=1740533602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 探索 20 多个闹鬼地点，其中有 15 种不同类型的地点，同时体验不同的天气状况</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162260/extras/e239d6c2e5886c3b63e2deb77b0cf8af.poster.avif?t=1740533602\" width=442 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162260/extras/e239d6c2e5886c3b63e2deb77b0cf8af.webm?t=1740533602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162260/extras/e239d6c2e5886c3b63e2deb77b0cf8af.mp4?t=1740533602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 了解 10 类证据，为驱鬼仪式提供依据。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - 体验众多超自然事件，努力求生存</p>",
